readable.content: A basketball player looks upward as a hand reaches for her ball . A female basketball player wearing a red uniform is holding a basketball and looking up while an arm is trying to block her . A female woman has a basketball in her hands and a determined look on her face . A woman basketball player holding the ball grimaces with effort while another player 's arm attempts to block her . A woman with a red basketball jersey is holding a basketball and looking up .
